WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: UZbTNDsiLDY

NOTE Language: en

00:00:05.073 --> 00:00:07.906
On behalf of all of you

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:13.107
Sahaja Yogi organisers of Bombay who have made these arrangements

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:16.507
I thank them all.

00:00:16.640 --> 00:00:25.640
And on my own behalf also, I thank them a lot. A very beautiful place.

00:00:25.774 --> 00:00:32.374
They have chosen a beautiful place for us.

00:00:32.507 --> 00:00:35.574
This is also God's grace

00:00:35.674 --> 00:00:37.841
that the thing about which I was going to speak

00:00:37.973 --> 00:00:42.674
sitting under the same trees, the
talk about Sahastrara is taking place.

00:00:42.807 --> 00:00:45.674
Fourteen years ago, we should say

00:00:45.807 --> 00:00:48.873
or thirteen years have already passed

00:00:49.006 --> 00:00:51.741
and now the fourteenth year has started.

00:00:51.841 --> 00:00:59.607
This great work was accomplished in
the world, when Sahastrara was opened.

00:00:59.741 --> 00:01:04.640
I have told you about this many times, on every Sahasrara day

00:01:04.741 --> 00:01:15.307
that what had happened? How it was done and what is its importance?

00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:19.574
But the fourteenth birthday is very important.

00:01:19.674 --> 00:01:22.774
Because man lives at fourteen levels

00:01:22.873 --> 00:01:29.307
and the day he crosses over the fourteenth
level, he becomes a complete Sahaja Yogi.

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:35.006
So, today Sahaja Yoga has also become Sahaja Yogi.

00:01:35.140 --> 00:01:40.507
Like this, God has created fourteen levels within you.

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:44.340
If you count these in an ordinary way

00:01:44.440 --> 00:01:50.674
then you know that, there are seven Chakras within us.

00:01:50.774 --> 00:01:54.207
Apart from these, the two more Chakras that are there

00:01:54.307 --> 00:01:59.006
about which, you do not talk much

00:01:59.107 --> 00:02:03.474
is the chakra of Chandra and that of Surya.

00:02:03.607 --> 00:02:05.741
Then there is 'Hamsa Chara'.

00:02:05.841 --> 00:02:08.841
Then there are three more chakras.

00:02:08.973 --> 00:02:12.607
Seven and three make ten.

00:02:12.707 --> 00:02:17.173
Then above that there are four chakras.

00:02:17.307 --> 00:02:19.774
Then there are four chakras above Sahastrara.

00:02:19.906 --> 00:02:23.273
And I have told you about these chakras also.

00:02:23.407 --> 00:02:32.440
Ardhabindu, Bindu, V alaya and Pradakhshina.

00:02:32.574 --> 00:02:35.873
These are four chakras.

00:02:35.973 --> 00:02:39.707
Even after Sahajyoga, when your Sahastrara has opened

00:02:39.841 --> 00:02:44.440
you have to pass through these four chakras.

00:02:44.574 --> 00:02:50.841
Ardhabindu, Bindu, Valaya and Pradakhshina.

00:02:50.973 --> 00:02:58.841
After these four chakras, we can say that we have become Sahaj yogi.

00:02:58.973 --> 00:03:01.741
But you see from the other angle also.

00:03:01.841 --> 00:03:07.273
We have to cross fourteen stages to reach up to Sahastrara

00:03:07.407 --> 00:03:09.107
if we divide these.

00:03:09.240 --> 00:03:14.240
Seven chakras are situated on Ida Nadi and seven on Pingala Nadi.

00:03:14.374 --> 00:03:18.640
When man ascends, he does not do so in a straight direction.

00:03:18.741 --> 00:03:24.006
He comes first to the left, then to the right

00:03:24.140 --> 00:03:26.674
then again to the left, and then to the right.

00:03:26.807 --> 00:03:34.973
And when Kundalini ascends, She also
does so, dividing Herself into these two.

00:03:35.107 --> 00:03:39.640
The reason for it is: If I make you to understand

00:03:39.774 --> 00:03:43.140
that there are two ropes.

00:03:43.273 --> 00:03:52.307
These two ropes, during the process of
coming down or going up, cross over twice.

00:03:52.440 --> 00:03:54.741
When it crosses twice

00:03:54.841 --> 00:04:00.873
then its left and right this way, first left and then right

00:04:01.006 --> 00:04:03.040
because of the crossing over of both

00:04:03.173 --> 00:04:06.574
the right one goes to the right and left one to the right.

00:04:06.707 --> 00:04:11.574
Now if we see this, I can show you, suppose it came this way

00:04:11.707 --> 00:04:12.707
Now it has taken one round

00:04:12.841 --> 00:04:16.374
and to take second round has come again by the same route

00:04:16.474 --> 00:04:19.607
It came this way and has taken one round and the another round.

00:04:19.707 --> 00:04:22.340
In this way it crosses twice.

00:04:22.440 --> 00:04:29.841
When Kundalini ascends, you see on the chakra
whether the left is caught or the right is caught.

00:04:29.973 --> 00:04:34.474
Because Kundalini is only one, but on
every chakra you see both the things.

00:04:34.574 --> 00:04:35.973
See in this way

00:04:36.107 --> 00:04:39.040
whether left is caught up or the right.

00:04:39.140 --> 00:04:43.540
Thus within us, if each chakra is divided into two, left and right

00:04:43.640 --> 00:04:45.707
then seven into two, is equal to fourteen.

00:04:45.807 --> 00:04:56.040
So, within us fourteen stages have to
be crossed before reaching Sahastrara.

00:04:56.173 --> 00:05:02.140
And if you understand this, that these seven, and seven above.

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:05.006
Then in this way also, a path of fourteen is created.

00:05:05.140 --> 00:05:12.173
So this number fourteen in Kundalini
shastra is very important, very important!

00:05:12.307 --> 00:05:14.774
Very important!

00:05:14.906 --> 00:05:18.107
And until we understand fully

00:05:18.240 --> 00:05:21.440
that when we will ascend above these fourteen stages

00:05:21.540 --> 00:05:24.540
then only,we become entitled to the blessings of Sahaja Yoga.

00:05:24.674 --> 00:05:30.707
We should march forward unceasingly
and get completely involved into it.

00:05:30.807 --> 00:05:36.407
'Rajna, virajna' – these words I have said many a times earlier also.

00:05:36.507 --> 00:05:42.474
But today specially, we should understand that on the Sahastrara day

00:05:42.574 --> 00:05:46.200
what is Rajna (to be the master) and what is Virajna (to assume)?